Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.06,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}对你的思念也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:49.76,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}是啊 也变得一场空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:52.91,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}不走运的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:02:00.14,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}也许会成为好机遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:07.31,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}若能见到你的笑脸 一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:11.94,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}成为猫咪 向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.56,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,100)}真可谓 MEOWDERFUL！
